Version 0.8.4 (2011-11-16):

    * Added standard --pidfile=path option. The file is opened exclusive.

    * The process can now (permanent or temporary) drop privileges between
      each process scanning by setting the UID and GID.

Version 0.8.3 (2011-11-16):

    * Fixed an automake problem manifesting itself when installing from Gentoo
      portage. The symbolic link in /usr/sbin were named programd.

    * The ebuild file is now bundled with the source code.

Version 0.8.2 (2011-11-16):

    * Custom script can now be executed along with signaling the process.

    * The application will function as a daemon process if started as procmond.

    * Added procmon (1) and procmond (8) manual page.

Version 0.8.1 (2011-11-16):
    
    * Added dry-run mode (-m).

Version 0.8.0 (2011-11-16):

    * Initial release.
